%h1 Why using link href?
%ul
  %li nice formatting
  %li no need of additional javascript files
  %li same button for each language (cause no text inside button)
  %li no load-jumping

%h1 Why not using link href?
%ul
  %li some troubles with empty spaces which has to be detected first (mail, google+,)
  %li window which opens is not that nice
  %li link solution is hacky (not supported by provider) 
